des:
Through Alexa you can listen to the best of rock non-stop.
Plus Radio Rock
Skill aimed at English-speaking users.
With Portuguese version.

To start say:

Alexa, open more rock
Alexa, open more rock
Alexa, play more rock
Alexa, play more rock


To stop say:

Alexa, stop
Alexa, cancel
